								<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SNeBCP+Logo.jpg" rel="&quot;lightbox&quot;&quot;"><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-4603" title="call center companies in Manila" src="http://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SNeBCP+Logo-208x300.jpg" alt="" width="208" height="300" srcset="https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SNeBCP+Logo-208x300.jpg 208w, https://www.fusionbposervices.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/SNeBCP+Logo.jpg 278w" sizes="(max-width: 208px) 100vw, 208px" /></a>BPO Manila understands how much the contemporary business enterprises need newer and better tools for sales lead generation. To fulfill the increased lead requirements of their clients they have turned social media into a really active and happening ground for sales lead generation.<br />
