<p>Let us first figure out why the Manila BPO industry opts for social media. A look at the number of visitors Facebook, Twitter and many others social network sites have each day answers all the riddles. Any promotional activity in the social media forum is bound to catch the maximum attention and that too in almost no time. The process is inexpensive and at the same time the results can be delivered faster.</p>
